  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: Docker image with tag `ethereum/client-go:alltools-latest`\r\nOS & Version: `Linux ubuntu-s-1vcpu-2gb-tor1-01 4.15.0-135-generic #139-Ubuntu SMP Mon Jan 18 17:38:24 UTC 2021 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux`\r\nCommit hash : [`43458f`](https://github.com/Gravity-Tech/gateway/commit/43458f24873fd3df90b392a1c17785883875f2a0)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nSuccessful *.abi files generation due to a fact that correct version of solc is already installed.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nFatal: Failed to build Solidity contract: exec: \"solc\": executable file not found in $PATH\r\nFatal: Failed to build Solidity contract: exec: \"solc\": executable file not found in $PATH\r\nmake: *** [Makefile:7: ethereum] Error 1\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\n1. Visit https://github.com/Gravity-Tech/gateway/tree/add-docker\r\n2. git clone https://github.com/Gravity-Tech/gateway.git\r\n3. cd gateway/\r\n4. git checkout add-docker\r\n5. docker build -t gateway-tests .\r\n6. docker run gateway-tests\r\n\r\n",
